title: SRA Submission - CEABIGR WGBS and RNA-seq

yaml.author: Sam White
yaml.title: SRA Submission - CEABIGR WGBS and RNA-seq

markdown.markdown:
Finally got around to getting the [CEABIGR](https://github.com/sr320/ceabigr) (GitHub repo) sequencing data uploaded to [NCBI's Short Read Archive (SRA)](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra). Data transfer took quite awhile, as we have both whole genome bisulfite (WGBS) and RNA-seq data for this project. Once that was completed, I filled out the required metadata and completed the submission.

The data is now available in the SRA, under BioProject [PRJNA1089235](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra/PRJNA1089235). Will get accessions added to [`Nightingales`](https://b.link/nightingales) (Google Sheet).
